Package io.opencaesar.oml

Interface ConceptInstanceReference

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DescriptionMemberReference, DescriptionStatement, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NamedInstanceReference, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Reference, Statement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConceptInstanceReferenceImpl
    public interface ConceptInstanceReference
extends NamedInstanceReference
    A representation of the model object 'Concept Instance Reference'. ConceptInstanceReference is a reference to a concept instance in some description, in order to add other types to it

    The following features are supported:

    • Instance
    • Owned Types
